<div class="content-card">
  <h1>About ArtForYou</h1>

  <p class="section-subtext">
    ArtForYou is a full-stack web application designed to showcase and manage a digital art collection.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <p>
      This project was developed as part of a full-stack web development program, with a focus on building a complete
      e-commerce-style experience from database to user interface.
    </p>

    <p>
      Key features of the application include:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Product browsing and category filtering</li>
      <li>Search and sorting functionality</li>
      <li>Shopping cart with session management</li>
      <li>Checkout flow with tax calculations by province</li>
      <li>Order creation and confirmation system</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      The goal of this project is to demonstrate practical skills in Ruby on Rails, database design,
      and responsive UI development.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="product-actions" style="margin-top: 24px;">
    <%= link_to "Back to Home", root_path, class: "button-link secondary-button" %>
  </div>
</div>